{
  "stem": "19923.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was all in Hebrew, nothing in German, nothing in Yiddish-- just all Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you would sit there endlessly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as a young child, I was bored stiff to the constant davening that was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nobody knew what was going on or what they were saying, but it was ritual.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- in my-- in my earliest times, I said, if I ever do this, it's going to be done so everybody will understand.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the Jews in those days, when they had Passover meals, there was a-- it was a long, drawn out affair.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The children hated it [LAUGHS] because you couldn't understand anything that was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The food was great when you finally got around to eating it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But in terms of what-- understanding what was going on around you, nobody did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My recollection of my father-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --you have to remember that I was eight years old when I last saw my father.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what I do recollect from him is that he was not an educated man and did not have any skills.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was an itinerant worker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Itinerant worker means he held jobs every once in a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I found out later in life that he had worked part time at a lumber yard and half the time he was on the public dole, that is on charity.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when-- even when he was working, he didn't make much money and we always had to have assistance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And assistance like, for instance, the shoes would be handed down from older child to younger child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When pairs of shoes were done, he would-- my father would go and get heels and he'd put the heels on himself on the shoes to repair them.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
